## 八、Module not found: Can't resolve 'private-next-pages/_app.js'

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8088864/59267395-bd396780-8c7c-11e9-9e5e-a7246d2936dd.png)

> 解决办法
修改 `next.config.js` 文件

```  next.config.js
// https://github.com/zeit/next.js/issues/6681

webpack(config) {
  config.resolve.alias = {
    ...config.resolve.alias,
    // your aliases
  }
}
```
